				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$x^{k}$\end{document}xk of the feasible set of (Pρ), the iteration at \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
